title: AUG_2016_Restart
description: Model details (10OCT2023) Version 6.3.1 - Model developer: HDR Engineering, Inc.    (Modeling lead: Ric McCallan) - Units: Horizontal and vertical units in US Feet - Horizontal Datum: North American Datum 1983, 2011 adjustment (NAD83 (2011))   - Restart run for August 2016 event.  - Infiltration included, no precipitation or wind included  - Steady state Variable stage boundary conditions included for downstream Gulf boundary. - Steady state flow hydrograph included for the Main Atchafalaya Channel at Simmesport, LA. - 2012 Existing Conditions Geometry - base grid cells 1000x1000, refinement included for streams and other key terrain features.  - Time step controlled by courant condition
